---
title: Pork Chops and Creamy Mustard Sauce with Arugula, Feta and Tomato Salad
description: Our velvety Dijon sauce is a perfect match for pork chops. Served over a salad of peppery arugula with creamy avocados, ripe baby tomatoes and crumbly feta.
